            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent-gold font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Step 2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary-plum mb-2">Upload &amp; analyse</h3>
        <p class="text-primary-mauve text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Upload your photo or use your camera. Our AI analyses your skin, hair and eye colors instantly.
